data.description: Great curb appeal welcomes you as you approach the front porch.  Upon entering the home you'll notice the gleaming hardwood floors in the large LR.  The eat-in kitchen includes new vinyl plank flooring and SS appliances.  The hardwood floors continue upstairs into all 3 BR's.  The basement has a large room that is currently used as a 4th BR and this space could be made into an expansive man cave or family room.  Separate laundry area and a half bath are also on the lower level.  Newly painted, furnace 2019, A/C July 2022, hot water tank 2017, roof 2016. Access the 2-level yard via the kitchen. Taxes are from Realist. One year home warranty. Being sold AS IS. Home inspection is for informational purposes only. NO REPAIRS
